room_title: Escape room "Spy Trainer" by Exit Strategy in Charlotte
room_description: You and your fellow agents have been handpicked to take part in the final selection stages for the most elite spy organization in the world. As this is a division that does not exist, operated by people who do not exist, should you fail, any memories of the experiences related to your time here will, likewise, cease to exist. Will you prove yourself worthy, or will you disappear in the shadows?
